channel.title: Last week
channel.description:
i told this story in serevre dev but it was deleted here you go
last week me and my friends were at the bus stop waiting for our bus when a car swerved from around the corner and crashed into a bunch of people from my school about 5 were hit and 1 is still on life support. yeh i took sum cool pics and sold em to the media. thats my cool story. ps this happened in queensland australia on sandgate road (brisbaners might know about this but just to say i was there)
